No.

297
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,900
Just came to say hi.

298
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,360
Let's get this done quickly.

299
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:15,760
Okay.

300
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:16,910
-Okay.
-Go ahead.

301
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:17,770
The food.

302
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,840
You eat, Chief Zhang.

303
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,970
I've already eaten.

304
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:34,280
Happy birthday!

305
00:11:36,290 --> 00:11:38,210
[Zhou Rong, Chairman of Rongcheng Group]

306
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:43,170
Ye still isn't here?

307
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,640
You know him.

308
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,390
He's a civil servant.

309
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,500
He can't make it.

310
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,690
Isn't he about to become

311
00:11:49,690 --> 00:11:50,690
the deputy chief?

312
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,650
Who can stop him

313
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:52,820
from coming to have a casual meal?

314
00:11:52,570 --> 00:11:54,510
[Lang Bowen, General Manager of Aotu]

315
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,310
What's wrong?

316
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:01,300
[Hu Jianren, Secretary of the Chairman
of Rongcheng Group]

317
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,680
Mr. Rong,

318
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,270
I heard

319
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,380
the province has assigned

320
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:06,100
a new police chief
of criminal investigations.

321
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:09,030
Assigned a new person?

322
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,300
From the province?

323
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,690
Where did you hear that?

324
00:12:13,690 --> 00:12:15,200
It's already been publicly announced.

325
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,750
The new chief's name is

326
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:17,590
Zhang Yi'ang.

327
00:12:17,810 --> 00:12:19,470
[Lu Yibo, General Manager
of Fenglin Night Hotel]

328
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:19,440
Zhang Yi'ang...

329
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:21,990
Zhang Yi'ang?

330
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:23,650
Have I heard this name before?

331
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,350
Yes.

332
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,240
He used to live

333
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,200
in Sanjiangkou.

334
00:12:28,630 --> 00:12:29,320
Is it that

335
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,340
"doubt the doubt of the doubt"?

336
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:31,930
Yes.

337
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,150
What kind of wind

338
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:38,010
blew this doubtful guy over here?

339
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:38,910
Well,

340
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,480
I wouldn't know.

341
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:43,960
Bowen.

342
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,610
I have a good bottle of wine.

343
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:47,330
Come get it.

344
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:51,840
Come, Yangyang.

345
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:53,120
Ren.

346
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,040
Come, Ren.

347
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:54,610
Cheers.

348
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,670
Ye has

349
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,270
suffered in Sanjiangkou
for so many years.

350
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:26,400
He should have made it to the top by now.

351
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,080
Why is there a new person now?

352
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,600
I told him to build some connections
long ago,

353
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,200
but he just wouldn't listen.

354
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:35,390
Didn't you understand what I meant?

355
00:13:37,010 --> 00:13:38,310
I was saying...

356
00:13:42,450 --> 00:13:43,170
Mr. Rong,

357
00:13:44,030 --> 00:13:45,360
no need to be so nervous.

358
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,880
It's just a new chief, isn't it?

359
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:59,930
[Ye Jian]
[I can't come. Happy birthday from afar.]

360
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,660
A deputy chief came

361
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:06,080
and he's immediately staying away
to avoid suspicion.

362
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,720
Why?

363
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,690
That matter was very clear.

364
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,200
It had absolutely nothing to do with us.

365
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:12,600
Ye said

366
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,790
they investigated it clearly.

367
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,520
No, what kind of person is Ye?

368
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,490
He's our bro.

369
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,590
That's true,

370
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,790
but Ye is also a cop.

371
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,360
Then let me put it this way,

372
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,490
if you broke the law,

373
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:25,910
based on emotion,

374
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,240
do you think Ye would let you go?

375
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:40,390
Hey,

376
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:41,670
I just don't understand.

377
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,510
Why can't we stay

378
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:44,910
[Lintao Motel]

379
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,870
without an ID?

380
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,080
I'm the one staying here,

381
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,190
not the ID card.

382
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,170
This is the rule.

383
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:51,730
I predict

384
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,720
the motel business will get harder

385
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,870
because these rules are getting stricter.

386
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:56,740
During the day,

387
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,180
we already suffered in the train aisle

388
00:14:58,180 --> 00:14:59,020
for hours.

389
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,040
At night,

390
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:02,030
we can't just sleep on the street, right?

391
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:02,840
Even if we stay in a hotel,

392
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,750
the money we have

393
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,280
is only enough for two days.

394
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,180
Then we need to get money quickly.

395
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,550
As for getting money,

396
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,150
I've already figured it out.

397
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:17,360
[Chuanshi Antique Collections]

398
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,700
Are we selling the goods here?

399
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,670
But you make a good point.

400
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:24,410
Not resting well

401
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:25,640
will affect our work.

402
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:28,050
I believe in this world,

403
00:15:28,050 --> 00:15:29,390
there are always people like us

404
00:15:28,690 --> 00:15:30,460
[Dayou Motel]

405
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:32,050
who run hotels and don't follow the rules.

406
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:33,530
[Pingshun Motel]

407
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:34,750
[Motel]

408
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:41,740
[Peach]

409
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,450
Two rooms?

410
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,080
One.

411
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,080
This is a love hotel.

412
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,240
There's only one bed.

413
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,370
And it's a waterbed.

414
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,720
Motorized.

415
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:54,170
As long as we can sleep.

416
00:15:58,260 --> 00:15:59,790
ID cards for registration.

417
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:06,480
We left in a hurry and forgot them.

418
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:09,140
Fifty extra per person without an ID.

419
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:09,870
That's a rip-off.

420
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:11,200
A hundred extra for two?

421
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:14,950
Calculated per day.
Are you staying or not?

422
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,240
Yes.

423
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:32,090
I told Song Xing

424
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:33,440
we'll start investigating

425
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,970
Chief Lu's case file today.

426
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,360
Song Xing said

427
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,270
he wouldn't be back until noon

428
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:38,670
to help us pull the files.

429
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:40,510
Aren't they supposed to fully

430
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,570
cooperate with us?

431
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:43,000
He said they're short-handed.

432
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:43,960
He and Captain Ye went to

433
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:46,090
the traffic police team for a meeting.

434
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,150
Assisting the traffic police?

435
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:50,150
Great, great, great.

436
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:55,090
Much better.

437
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:55,880
Much better.

438
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:01,990
[Chuanshi Antique Collections]

439
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:04,670
♪ Burning on its own
somewhere between haziness and clarity ♪

440
00:17:02,020 --> 00:17:04,780
[Peach Night Hotel]

441
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:12,109
[Chuanshi Antique Collections]

442
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:14,790
♪ In the careless detail,
he touched the color ♪

443
00:17:18,890 --> 00:17:21,160
♪ The show starts getting interesting ♪

444
00:17:23,339 --> 00:17:25,460
♪ I wonder who's the real onlooker here ♪

445
00:17:27,619 --> 00:17:29,610
♪ Find the onlooker ♪

446
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,990
It's authentic, but...

447
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:41,320
[Zheng Yongbing, Independent Collector]

448
00:17:37,510 --> 00:17:38,380
My friends,

449
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:40,920
do you have receipts for these?

450
00:17:42,030 --> 00:17:43,240
What if we do?

451
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,740
What if we don't?

452
00:17:45,850 --> 00:17:48,550
There was an explosion
in the provincial capital a few days ago.

453
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,610
Haven't you heard?

454
00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:53,630
And then?

455
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,740
A jewelry store

456
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,420
was robbed by a man and a woman.

457
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:57,930
We're both men.

458
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:58,790
Yes.

459
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,830
I'm just afraid

460
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:02,910
they are from a questionable source.

461
00:18:07,330 --> 00:18:08,660
Can you take them or not?

462
00:18:13,810 --> 00:18:14,990
Take it easy.

463
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:16,660
I can.

464
00:18:17,690 --> 00:18:18,350
I can.

465
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:21,200
It's not easy for us to do business.

466
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,100
Since you can take it,

467
00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:28,440
take this too.

468
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,350
This stone statue...

469
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,400
What is it made of?

470
00:18:45,150 --> 00:18:45,780
Jade.

471
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:47,370
A jade statue.

472
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:52,790
My friends,

473
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,860
how much do you want for it?

474
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:09,270
Chief,

475
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:10,750
the first interrogation

476
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:11,880
of the offending driver

477
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,210
was indeed not recorded

478
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,200
because the bureau's system

479
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,440
was being upgraded at the time.

480
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,800
We weren't familiar with it yet,

481
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:17,860
so it wasn't saved.

482
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,240
Other than the first interrogation,

483
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,900
the rest of the files are here.

484
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:23,680
So many.

485
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:26,350
The archive room's fire safety system
is being upgraded,

486
00:19:26,350 --> 00:19:27,310
so the files are temporarily stored

487
00:19:27,310 --> 00:19:28,570
in the warehouse here.

488
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:30,110
To find the files for Chief Lu's case,

489
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:31,830
you'll have to rely on yourself.

490
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:32,550
Or...

491
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:34,110
you can wait half a month.

492
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,510
Once the archive room is sorted out,

493
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:36,910
it'll be easier to find things.

494
00:19:36,910 --> 00:19:37,640
Half a month?

495
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:40,300
Was the archive room

496
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,900
upgraded on short notice?

497
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,050
For the specifics,

498
00:19:45,050 --> 00:19:47,270
you'll have to ask
Chief Qi and Captain Ye.

499
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,270
There are so many.

500
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:49,480
We need some manpower

501
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,340
to help us look.

502
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:51,790
There is definitely no manpower available.

503
00:19:51,790 --> 00:19:53,070
Captain Ye took everyone in the bureau

504
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,800
for the DUI operation tonight.

505
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,610
Chen's Chicken Racks.

506
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:04,090
I'm talking about Chen's Chicken Racks.

507
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:04,920
Their chicken racks

508
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,270
take 40 minutes to fry.

509
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:07,800
You even have to wait in line.

510
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,730
I'll take you to try it another day.

511
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:10,790
If you are really busy,

512
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,310
you wouldn't spend two hours

513
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:13,270
at noon

514
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:15,040
just to eat some chicken racks.

515
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:19,110
How did you know

516
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:20,170
I was eating there?

517
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,600
I know all the good food in Sanjiangkou.

518
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:26,110
I still remember the flavors

519
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:27,360
of the few barbecue shops,

520
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,290
especially Chen's Chicken Racks.

521
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:32,280
Can't believe they haven't
changed the chef.

522
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:37,840
As for me,

523
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:41,020
I came to Sanjiangkou out of nowhere.

524
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:43,610
The comrades don't trust me much.

525
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,640
I can understand.

526
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,230
But if it delays work,

527
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:48,970
that won't be good, right?

528
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:52,950
I'll help you find it.

529
00:20:52,950 --> 00:20:53,670
No need.

530
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,180
This will deepen the comrades'

531
00:20:55,180 --> 00:20:56,580
misunderstanding of me.

532
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,260
Go do your work.

533
00:20:59,270 --> 00:20:59,800
Go ahead.

534
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:09,720
Chief,

535
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:10,590
I'll look for it.

536
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:11,750
You go watch the video.

537
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:12,680
Can you do it alone?

538
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,410
Don't worry.

539
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:16,230
Okay.

540
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:37,110
Okay.

541
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:38,790
One.

542
00:21:40,090 --> 00:21:41,180
Push.

543
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,900
Watch your breathing.

544
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,210
Okay, squeeze.

545
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,320
Good, very good.

546
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:49,400
Okay, push.

547
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,090
Go, exhale.

548
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:52,550
Squeeze.

549
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,700
-Come on. Go on.
-Mr. Rong.

550
00:21:55,780 --> 00:21:57,110
Time for your medicine.

551
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:58,550
Why only one pill?

552
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,050
You've been working out for a while.

553
00:22:00,050 --> 00:22:01,480
You've let off enough steam.

554
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,880
The doctor said you have bipolar disorder.

555
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:04,670
You can't just rely on medication.

556
00:22:04,670 --> 00:22:06,470
I have too many things on my mind.

557
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:07,640
Since Bowen got

558
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,720
the Aotu subsidiary,

559
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,180
he's gotten a lot of ideas.

560
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,890
Yibo runs Fenglin Night

561
00:22:12,070 --> 00:22:14,330
and revolves around his woman every day.

562
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:17,040
That guy named Zhang got transferred back.

563
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,370
Nothing is going right.

564
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:24,750
Did you find out why Zhang

565
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,420
came back to Sanjiangkou?

566
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,400
No.

567
00:22:27,810 --> 00:22:29,680
Should we ask Captain Ye?

568
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:31,200
Absolutely not.

569
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,050
When Lu was alive,

570
00:22:33,310 --> 00:22:34,200
he thought Ye and I

571
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,750
were trading money for power.

572
00:22:35,750 --> 00:22:37,200
We're just friends who grew up together.

573
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,720
Can't cause trouble for him.

574
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,180
You value relationships.

575
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,200
Mr. Rong,

576
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,750
if anything else happens,

577
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:44,610
I'll still take the blame for you.

578
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,470
Jianren.

579
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:50,240
We've known each other the shortest,

580
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,040
but in the end,

581
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:53,010
you're the most reliable.

582
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:57,510
Mr. Rong.

583
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,760
We've been a bit unlucky lately.

584
00:23:01,510 --> 00:23:03,110
Should I hire a fengshui master?

585
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,030
We can spend some money.

586
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:05,640
As the saying goes,
money prevents disasters.

587
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,970
Let's fix the fengshui.

588
00:23:07,290 --> 00:23:07,830
Okay.

589
00:23:08,590 --> 00:23:09,790
You handle this.

590
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:11,890
Shuangshuang!

591
00:23:12,890 --> 00:23:13,520
Come on.

592
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:15,430
You've gotten stronger recently.

593
00:23:15,430 --> 00:23:16,430
Adjust this rope.

594
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,010
Okay, go.

595
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:21,590
One.

596
00:23:22,830 --> 00:23:23,350
Two.

597
00:23:24,010 --> 00:23:25,270
Watch your breathing.

598
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,520
Go, squeeze.

599
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:38,090
[Anzhi Road, Sanjiangkou City,
Ping'an Province]

600
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,340
Come in.

601
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,960
I've finished reading.

602
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:58,600
That fast?

603
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,810
Inspired by you.

604
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:00,350
If someone

605
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:01,640
wanted to make things difficult for us,

606
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,590
they would definitely hide the files

607
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,600
in the very back.

608
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,550
I went straight to the boxes in the back,

609
00:24:05,550 --> 00:24:06,880
and found them quickly.

610
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,480
The driver who caused the accident
is Shen Gang.

611
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:12,020
The file clearly records that

612
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:12,940
[List of Road Traffic Accident]

613
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,800
as he was approaching the intersection,

614
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:14,680
he was blinded by the high beams

615
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,760
of an oncoming vehicle.

616
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:16,600
He didn't see

617
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,590
the intersection light

618
00:24:17,590 --> 00:24:18,680
turn red,

619
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,460
so he hit Chief Lu.

620
00:24:21,060 --> 00:24:22,750
The police handling the case
previously suspected

621
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:23,590
that the driver who flashed high beams

622
00:24:23,590 --> 00:24:24,980
at Shen Gang

623
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,930
might have had an ulterior motive.

624
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:28,450
Later, it was verified

625
00:24:28,450 --> 00:24:30,180
that it was indeed an accident.

626
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,870
But I think

627
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:34,070
it's still necessary to have Shen Gang

628
00:24:34,070 --> 00:24:35,000
come over again.

629
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,640
They must've already asked

630
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,500
many questions about the driver.

631
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,200
Having Shen Gang come over

632
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:46,200
probably won't get us anything new.

633
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:47,590
I really want to find this driver

634
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:48,680
who turned on the high beams.

635
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,480
and bring him in for questioning again.

636
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,680
The driver with the high beams?

637
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,750
They already asked him too.

638
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:53,550
Ask him again.

639
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,660
We're just verifying.

640
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:04,380
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

641
00:25:02,410 --> 00:25:03,020
Come in.

642
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,440
This operation against

643
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,290
drunk driving

644
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:12,070
is led by the Traffic Police Department,

645
00:25:12,070 --> 00:25:13,200
and supported by the CID.

646
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,530
It's a joint operation.

647
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:16,430
I will supervise the team.

648
00:25:16,570 --> 00:25:18,330
We'll act at 7:00 PM tonight.

649
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:19,560
Now, let me

650
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,590
assign the tasks.

651
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:21,490
My car

652
00:25:22,230 --> 00:25:23,360
is fully automatic.

653
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,250
It's really annoying.

654
00:25:25,340 --> 00:25:26,080
That day,

655
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,020
it was raining,

656
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:28,950
and the road was dark.

657
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:30,710
It's a flagship SUV.

658
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:31,880
Fully automatic!

659
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:34,280
It just turned the high beams on
automatically.

660
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:35,760
Maybe

661
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:37,160
it shined on that guy.

662
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:39,510
I... I already told you

663
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,710
about this last time.

664
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:42,160
Who knows

665
00:25:42,180 --> 00:25:43,880
if it really blinded him?

666
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:45,360
Right.

667
00:25:45,970 --> 00:25:47,170
If I were in his shoes,

668
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:49,150
I would definitely blame others.

669
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,610
But anyway,

670
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,860
this has nothing to do with me.

671
00:25:53,030 --> 00:25:54,260
It's automatic.

672
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:56,350
I didn't even know the high beams were on.

673
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,830
It was only later,

674
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,420
when your colleagues found me,

675
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,550
that I knew about it.

676
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:02,160
Tell me,

677
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:04,240
why did I buy this flagship SUV?

678
00:26:04,710 --> 00:26:06,310
It's even a parallel import.

679
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:07,640
Wasn't I just

680
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,840
looking for trouble?

681
00:26:16,330 --> 00:26:19,300
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

682
00:26:18,790 --> 00:26:19,490
Officers,

683
00:26:19,930 --> 00:26:21,240
ask me if you need anything else.

684
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:22,960
I will definitely cooperate with
the police.

685
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:23,560
Thank you.

686
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,390
Take care.

687
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:29,360
Let's watch the video of the scene again.

688
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,060
What about him?

689
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:38,640
He doesn't give off the vibe of a killer.

690
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,550
"Flagship SUV."

691
00:26:41,220 --> 00:26:43,020
He's good at shifting the blame.

692
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:46,720
[February 29, 2012]

693
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:48,300
At 7:00,

694
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,200
the operation will start on time.

695
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,350
Any questions?

696
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,130
Meeting adjourned.

697
00:27:00,130 --> 00:27:00,670
Wang,

698
00:27:03,280 --> 00:27:05,210
what is Zhang Yi'ang's team doing?

699
00:27:07,090 --> 00:27:08,110
They seem to be reviewing

700
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:11,640
the surveillance footage from the night
of Mentor's accident.

701
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:20,930
Is the man they just brought in

702
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,550
the driver who hit and killed

703
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:23,390
Director Lu?

704
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:24,000
No.

705
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:26,310
He's the driver with the high beams.

706
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:27,430
I remember him.

707
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:29,240
Always bragging about his flagship SUV.

708
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,400
But he's definitely not the killer.

709
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,800
He doesn't have the vibe.

710
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,220
I left my laptop inside.

711
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:36,880
You go back first.

712
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:37,240
Okay.

713
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:20,410
Zhang, I'm sending you a picture.

714
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,600
Enlarge it and make it clear.

715
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:38,960
Archive room,

716
00:28:39,480 --> 00:28:40,750
find all the cases

717
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:41,660
Director Lu was involved in

718
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,690
the year before he passed away.

719
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:43,290
Right now!

720
00:28:51,910 --> 00:28:54,640
[The World's Jokes]

721
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:03,790
Mr. Rong.

722
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,640
Let me ask you a question.

723
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,000
What animal

724
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:10,680
is the quietest

725
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,300
when it gets angry?

726
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:15,280
What animal?

727
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:16,310
Take a guess.

728
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:18,420
A shark?

729
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:19,660
A tiger?

730
00:29:20,070 --> 00:29:20,480
A pig?

731
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:20,960
No.

732
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:22,920
A bear.

733
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:23,960
A bear?

734
00:29:24,150 --> 00:29:24,630
Why?

735
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:27,090
Because when a bear

736
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,740
gets angry,

737
00:29:27,630 --> 00:29:30,810
[Global Jokes]

738
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:29,770
it's...

739
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:32,030
beary quiet.

740
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:40,720
Funny.

741
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,210
The doctor said

742
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:43,420
that laughing more

743
00:29:43,420 --> 00:29:44,890
is good for your health.

744
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,460
What were you going to say?

745
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,150
Mr. Rong, I've asked around.

746
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,100
The newcomer Zhang Yi'ang

747
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,700
used to work in the Veteran Cadre Bureau

748
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:56,430
of the provincial department.

749
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:00,610
Veteran Cadre Bureau?

750
00:30:00,610 --> 00:30:02,750
That's quite unexpected.

751
00:30:02,850 --> 00:30:03,550
But...

752
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,270
How could someone

753
00:30:05,590 --> 00:30:06,640
from the Veteran Cadre Bureau

754
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,360
come to Sanjiangkou

755
00:30:08,450 --> 00:30:09,710
to be the deputy chief?

756
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,030
Maybe he sucked up

757
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,200
to some old leader.

758
00:30:12,650 --> 00:30:13,650
That's not funny.

759
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,240
Don't be vulgar.

760
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,480
Rumor has it

761
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:23,740
that the provincial department
received a report letter.

762
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,130
What report letter?

763
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:27,630
Who did they report?

764
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:29,300
I'm not sure.

765
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:30,800
Only insiders know.

766
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:34,680
A report letter.

767
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,460
Who would they report?

768
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:45,590
Mr. Rong,

769
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,720
if you really want

770
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,080
to put your mind at ease,

771
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:50,450
I suggest

772
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:52,840
we still need to ask Captain Ye.

773
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,440
Even if it's indirect,

774
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:56,300
even if it's just having a meal...

775
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,660
Feel out his attitude.

776
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:04,910
[The World's Jokes]

777
00:31:24,460 --> 00:31:25,890
[Criminal Investigation File]

778
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,010
It's unrelated.

779
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:33,140
Why would he do this?

780
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:37,610
Captain Ye.

781
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,620
Captain Ye.

782
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:40,840
What is it?

783
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:41,880
I carefully studied

784
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:42,590
the traffic violation records

785
00:31:42,590 --> 00:31:43,440
from the last three months.

786
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,550
There were 12 cases of drunk driving,

787
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:45,310
23 cases of driving after drinking,

788
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,750
and 5 cases of driving without a license.

789
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:47,750
There were also unlicensed vehicles

790
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:48,750
and overloading.

791
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,420
What are you trying to say?

792
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,120
I think

793
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:52,720
our joint

794
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,750
city-wide DUI operation

795
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,030
with the traffic police brigade

796
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:56,560
should expand the key areas

797
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,110
to not only national
and provincial highways,

798
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,510
but also key rural roads.

799
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,950
The time frame should also be extended

800
00:32:00,950 --> 00:32:02,400
from midnight to morning.

801
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,400
We need to check not only night drinking

802
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,930
but also morning drinking.

803
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:06,270
Do you know how much manpower

804
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:08,130
this kind of check would require?

805
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,680
Use your brain!

806
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,300
I'm just

807
00:32:16,290 --> 00:32:18,220
thinking for the joint operation.

808
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,210
Chief Zhang.

809
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:31,160
Ye.

810
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:32,220
I'm feeling

811
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,780
a bit unwell.

812
00:32:34,070 --> 00:32:35,800
I'll leave tonight's DUI check

813
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:36,480
to you.

814
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:37,820
Is it the flu?

815
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,030
The flu.

816
00:32:41,810 --> 00:32:42,900
Ye,

817
00:32:43,590 --> 00:32:44,270
you're still more familiar

818
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,600
with the bureau's work.

819
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,240
We're here just to investigate

820
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,300
the report letter.

821
00:32:49,490 --> 00:32:51,690
Any new discoveries in Chief Lu's case?

822
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,440
Not yet.

823
00:32:52,980 --> 00:32:54,790
Still investigating.

824
00:32:55,030 --> 00:32:55,920
So you see,

825
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:57,270
we can't spare the time.

826
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:59,270
Won't you help me out with this,

827
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,050
Chief Zhang?

828
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,680
I didn't say I wouldn't help.

829
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,280
Thank you.

830
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:08,210
I didn't say I would either.

831
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:14,830
Captain Ye.

832
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:15,560
Going to eat?

833
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,110
The joint operation is at 7:00 tonight.

834
00:33:17,110 --> 00:33:17,910
Don't be late.

835
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:18,440
Okay.

836
00:33:25,350 --> 00:33:26,640
We must meet tonight.

837
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,440
I just want to ask you one question.

838
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,920
The night Lu Zheng had his accident,

839
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,780
where were you?

840
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:05,750
The comrades want to see
if I'm qualified to be the chief.

841
00:34:05,750 --> 00:34:06,830
They're making things more difficult

842
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:07,680
to test my qualifications

843
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,550
to be the chief.

844
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,530
I must withstand this test.

845
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:16,429
Can you withstand it?

846
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:19,320
Chief!

847
00:34:22,739 --> 00:34:23,960
I heard that the operation tonight

848
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,219
will be in your charge.

849
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,820
I have a small suggestion.

850
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:35,570
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau
DUI 100-Day Operation Plan]

851
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:33,480
This is so detailed.

852
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:34,960
You came prepared.

853
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:38,480
We'll execute according to this plan.

854
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:38,920
Yes.

855
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:43,489
[Loyalty]

856
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:42,449
Then let me emphasize two points.

857
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:43,360
One,

858
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:44,770
ideologically,

859
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:47,400
we must attach great importance to it.

860
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,710
We must always keep in mind

861
00:34:48,710 --> 00:34:49,590
our mission.

862
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,210
At the same time,

863
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,310
put down your burdens

864
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:54,760
and travel light.

865
00:34:54,989 --> 00:34:56,080
Empty your minds.

866
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:57,960
Two,

867
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,840
disciplinarily,

868
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,890
we must absolutely obey commands.

869
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:02,610
However,

870
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,700
we must not forget to be flexible.

871
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:07,920
A general in the field
is not bound by orders from the sovereign.

872
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:10,320
Everyone, please pay attention to safety.

873
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:16,270
That's it.

874
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:20,150
Let's go!

875
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:27,750
[Public Security]

876
00:35:32,090 --> 00:35:32,920
[Public Security]

877
00:35:32,950 --> 00:35:38,720
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

878
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:11,150
[Police]

879
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,360
Come this way.

880
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:14,900
